04:42.630 --> 04:44.790
Fall break, and here we sit.

04:46.180 --> 04:49.180
No plans, nothing to do.

04:49.890 --> 04:52.250
I've been warning you since September.

04:52.350 --> 04:55.380
Go to the beach,
go to the mountains, do something.

04:55.480 --> 04:57.340
Don't say I didn't tell you so.

04:57.440 --> 04:59.840
Well, why didn't you make
some reservations?

04:59.940 --> 05:00.970
I should have,

05:01.070 --> 05:03.450
but you guys never agree on anything.

05:04.110 --> 05:07.110
So, we'll sit around here
just like we did last year.

05:07.330 --> 05:09.080
It's depressing.

05:09.830 --> 05:12.460
Hey, Ed, uh, you have a telephone call.

05:13.540 --> 05:14.790
Right.

05:15.210 --> 05:17.170
No, seriously, you have a telephone call.

05:18.630 --> 05:20.050
Well, what do you know?

05:21.130 --> 05:23.300
Ralph said what he meant for a change.

05:27.090 --> 05:28.210
Yeah?

05:32.480 --> 05:33.730
My dad?

05:37.100 --> 05:39.180
Yeah, OK. Uh-huh.

05:39.360 --> 05:41.820
Well, anybody got
any good ideas for break?

05:43.070 --> 05:45.320
I'm gonna set a new high score
on the video machine.

05:45.530 --> 05:46.850
I'm gonna watch.

05:46.950 --> 05:47.950
How about you?

05:48.320 --> 05:51.900
Well, actually, I was relying on you
to make the arrangements.

05:52.500 --> 05:53.600
Oh, Ralph.

05:53.700 --> 05:55.110
Anybody got any paper?

05:55.210 --> 05:57.190
It's a message to call my dad.

05:57.290 --> 05:58.920
From a phone booth, for Christ's sakes.

06:03.840 --> 06:05.970
I thought Ed's father was dead.

06:06.760 --> 06:08.350
His mother is dead.

06:08.800 --> 06:11.210
God, it was a terrible accident, too.

06:11.470 --> 06:12.770
What happened?

06:13.890 --> 06:17.650
When he was a little boy,
Ed accidentally shot her.

06:18.100 --> 06:19.510
Oh, ho-ho, man...

06:20.270 --> 06:22.780
- Drove his father crazy.
- I can understand it.

06:23.400 --> 06:25.200
You know, I really can't...

06:26.450 --> 06:28.660
Dad?

06:31.450 --> 06:32.740
I don't believe it.

06:33.370 --> 06:34.370
Don't believe what?

06:35.160 --> 06:36.250
My old man.

06:36.370 --> 06:37.370
What's up?

06:37.920 --> 06:40.460
He's having another one of his spells.

06:40.750 --> 06:43.110
- What do you mean?
- Yeah, what kind of spells?

06:43.210 --> 06:44.800
The kind that come in bottles.

06:45.800 --> 06:47.530
Well, what's the problem?

06:47.630 --> 06:49.380
Will you let the man talk?

06:50.510 --> 06:53.330
He wants me to close up
his condo for the winter.

06:53.430 --> 06:55.210
Oh, that sounds like work.

06:55.310 --> 06:58.500
What's the matter?
Big strong you, afraid of a little work?

06:58.600 --> 07:02.210
Oh, he just has to save his strength
for more important things.

07:02.310 --> 07:04.020
- Right.
- It's not it.

07:04.400 --> 07:09.260
I mean, all my life the creep's ignored me,
and treated me like some redheaded bastard.

07:09.360 --> 07:10.560
Um...

07:10.660 --> 07:12.030
Oh, sorry.

07:13.410 --> 07:16.540
Now, all of a sudden, he calls me up
and asks me to do something.

07:17.040 --> 07:20.190
Tells me I'm old enough to
"take the responsibility."

07:20.290 --> 07:21.290
What'd you say?

07:21.420 --> 07:22.620
I told him to do his own work.

07:22.710 --> 07:23.840
What'd he say?

07:25.210 --> 07:27.920
He said if I didn't do it,
it wouldn't get done.

07:28.420 --> 07:30.040
"Face it like a man."

07:30.930 --> 07:33.310
And I'm not gonna do it.
I mean, what a jerk.

07:33.680 --> 07:35.100
How much work?

07:36.100 --> 07:38.580
"Turn off the water,
turn off the electricity,

07:38.680 --> 07:40.710
"pour some antifreeze in the plumbing."

07:40.810 --> 07:43.360
"Any 10-year-old can handle it."

08:03.460 --> 08:06.570
Uh, did you say,
any 10-year-old can handle it?

08:06.670 --> 08:08.360
- It's a snap.
- Nothing to it.

08:08.460 --> 08:09.370
We can handle that.

08:09.470 --> 08:11.910
Yeah, how come we didn't know
you had a condo at the beach?

08:12.010 --> 08:13.050
No way.

08:13.680 --> 08:15.370
What do you say?

08:15.470 --> 08:18.560
Four days of R&R at the beach.

08:18.810 --> 08:21.380
- I'm in.
- She's in, I'm in.

08:21.480 --> 08:22.480
Sounds good to me.

08:26.480 --> 08:29.110
I got a bad feeling about this.

08:42.539 --> 08:44.530
- Don't forget our arrangement.
- Oh!

08:44.630 --> 08:47.400
Oh, I'm sorry. Don't know
what I'm doing, you know? Just all...

08:47.500 --> 08:49.320
I really didn't mean to. OK?

08:49.420 --> 08:50.550
OK. Bye-bye.

08:53.130 --> 08:54.410
What's the matter, Ralph?

08:54.510 --> 08:56.580
Guys, Sue can't come.

08:56.680 --> 08:58.370
- No.
- Yeah.

08:58.470 --> 09:00.076
Something went wrong
with one of her exams,

09:00.100 --> 09:01.826
