have to take it over again.

09:01.850 --> 09:03.100
- Oh, God.
- That's terrible.

09:03.270 --> 09:06.440
- Yeah...
- Get in. You can't let that spoil your trip.

09:07.520 --> 09:10.380
- Where are you going?
- I'm just going in to say goodbye.

09:10.480 --> 09:13.270
Hey, no, guys, I really
wouldn't feel right going without Sue.

09:13.530 --> 09:15.310
- Don't be a jerk.
- Get in the car.

09:15.410 --> 09:17.270
You're going. No backing out now.

09:17.370 --> 09:18.886
- No...
- Get in the car. Get in the car.

09:18.910 --> 09:20.440
Hey, there's Sue.

09:20.540 --> 09:22.440
Hi, guys. Sorry to keep you waiting.

09:22.540 --> 09:23.610
Hi, Sue.

09:23.710 --> 09:25.440
I'm really sorry you can't go.

09:25.540 --> 09:27.440
- Yeah, me too.
- Rotten luck.

09:27.540 --> 09:29.290
What're you guys talking about?

09:31.010 --> 09:32.450
- Ralph!
- Ooh! Oh, man!

09:32.550 --> 09:33.550
What a jerk.

09:34.510 --> 09:36.830
God, I believe him
every time, all the time.

09:36.930 --> 09:39.160
- Guys, gimme a break.
- Aw, Ralph.

09:39.260 --> 09:42.460
Besides, let's get this road trip...

09:42.560 --> 09:43.790
